              "content": "=You are a professional social media content writer.\n\nWrite a {{ $json.platform }} post about the following topic.\n\nTopic: {{ $json.topic }}\nPlatform: {{ $json.platform }}\nScheduled Date: {{ $json.scheduledDate }}\nGuidelines: {{ $json.guidelines }}\n\nMake the post {{ $json.guidelines }}\n\nRespond in this exact format:\nCaption: [your caption here]\nHashtags: [your hashtags here]"
            }
