      "parameters": {
        "content": "📱 Social Media Content Scheduler Workflow\n\nReads content ideas from Google Sheets, uses AI to \nwrite platform optimized captions for LinkedIn, \nTwitter and Instagram and marks posts as scheduled.\n\nNodes:\n**Step 1**\n▶ Schedule Trigger — Runs every day at 7am\n\n**Step 2**\n📊 Google Sheets — Reads pending content ideas\n\n**Step 3**\n⚙️ Code in JavaScript — Adds platform guidelines per post\n\n**Step 4**\n🤖 OpenAI — Writes captions for each platform\n\n**Step 5**\n⚙️ Code in JavaScript1 — Cleans and structures AI output\n\n**Step 6**\n📧 Gmail — Creates draft posts for review\n\n**Step 7**\n⚙️ Code in JavaScript2 — Prepares status update data\n\n**Step 8**\n📊 Google Sheets1 — Marks posts as Scheduled",
